Ummm, its in the first thread immediately after telling you how to calculate DI (whihc you quote).  Anyway:<br>
<br>
DI = (max hit) - (min hit) / 19<br>
DB = (min hit) - DI <p>____________<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=13463"
