Superb work! Just one question, can it be taken further? The DB and DI numbers are very useful. However an even more interesting question is how much mitigation AC you require to get to modal 1 or, far more importantly, off modal 20.<br>
<br>
It would be nice to be able to look at some of the luclin mobs and determine if it is worth trying to add another 100 point of AC's. If it's still going to be on modal 20, no point, might as well get as many HP as you can. Whereas if you can get a lower modal damage that might be a lot less damage taken over the combat.<br>
<br>
It would be nice to have a universal form (calculate the ATK of the mob and then derive the AC values) but a pragmatic version would work as well in which various warriors note what AC they had and which number turned out to be the modal value.<br>
