<br>
Kick----Max hit 214-----min hit 201<br>
Bas----Max hit 212-----min hit 201<br>
Crush-Max hit 1100---min hit 222<br>
<br>
Ok max hit-min hit =1100-201=899<br>
DI = max-min/19   = 899/19=47.3<br>
DB=Min hit+DI      =201+47.3=248.3<br>
<br>
So this would make Statue:<br>
DB 248.3<br>
DI  47.3<br>
<br>
Is this correct?(I always sucked at math<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ) <p>
